" Set relative line numbering with absolute number for current line
set number relativenumber

" vim-commentary emulation
set commentary

" IDEA Actions
:map <leader>db <Action>(Debug)
:map <leader>rf <Action>(ReformatCode)
:map <leader>rn <Action>(RenameElement)
:map <leader>cd <Action>(GotoDeclaration)

" Kinesis bindings
" Press i to enter insert mode, and jk or kj to exit.
:imap jk <Esc>
:imap kj <Esc>

